title: H.S. Volleyball: Morris Hills Scarlet Knights win
text:
H.S. Volleyball: Morris Hills Scarlet Knights win October 21, 2015 Last updated: Wednesday, October 21, 2015, 12:31 AM Neighbor News (Denville Edition) Print 
Morris Hills girls volleyball team shut out Parsippany Hills’ Vikings, 2-0, on Oct. 9 in Rockaway. Here, Aziza Alamanakly slams a spike for Morris Hills over Jessica Zinckgraf and Kristi Ambrosino's defense. Morris Hills next home game will be against Sparta on Thursday, Oct. 22, at 4 p.m. It will also be the school’s Senior Day. Photos courtesy of JOHN C. MANNA © 2015 North Jersey Media Group Tags:
